WEBVTT

00:00:58.835 --> 00:01:00.474
in vivid colors.

00:01:00.498 --> 00:01:03.561
And if it were about superheroes instead?

00:01:04.470 --> 00:01:06.020
I would do them like this,

00:01:06.044 --> 00:01:09.955
inspired by -- in my opinion --
the greatest of all:

00:01:09.979 --> 00:01:11.533
Superman.

00:01:11.557 --> 00:01:13.051
(Laughter)

00:01:13.075 --> 00:01:16.256
The shapes of these letters talk.

00:01:17.219 --> 00:01:20.787
They tell us things
beyond what they represent.

00:01:21.751 --> 00:01:23.859
They send us to different eras,

00:01:23.883 --> 00:01:25.885
they convey values,

00:01:25.909 --> 00:01:28.029
they tell us stories.